('What is the purpose of access control lists (ACLs)?', 'Encrypt data', 'Define who can access resources', 'Monitor network traffic', 'Backup data', 'B', 'ACLs specify which users or systems can access specific resources.', 'Access Control'),
('What is single sign-on (SSO)?', 'One password for all users', 'One authentication for multiple systems', 'One user per system', 'One login attempt allowed', 'B', 'SSO allows users to authenticate once and access multiple systems.', 'Access Control'),
